reviewText: Not like the original Arabic Sesame Street. Whats annoying is that they use a lot of materials from the American culture and they also use English sometimes. This is not to say that American children songs are not good, but since this is in Arabic, why not use a few songs from the Arabian culture? If you're not creative enough, check out Iftah Ya Simsim that was produced over 20 years ago. I only bought this because I couldn't find the original. Im a little disappointed.
